  <main>
    
    <section class="flex flex-col mb-12 items-center">
      <h1 class="title">Irregular verbs</h1>
      <p>Choose the correct options:</p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mb-12">
      <p>ex: have - <span class="sub">had</span> / haved</p>
      <ol>
        <li>meet - meet (presente) / <span class="sub">met</span> (pasado)</li>
        <li>win - wan / <span class="sub">won</span></li>
        <li>lose - <span class="sub">lost</span> / losen</li>
        <li>buy - buyed / <span class="sub">bought</span></li>
        <li>eat - eat / <span class="sub">ate</span></li>
        <li>see - <span class="sub">saw</span> / sew</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <h1 class="title">Past simple: regular and irregular</h1>

    <section>
      <ol>
        <li>I <span class="sub">found</span> (find) the bag under the desk</li>
        <li>He <span class="sub">went</span> (go) there on holiday</li>
        <li>We <span class="sub">visited</span> (visit) the museum</li>
        <li>She <span class="sub">had</span> (have) pizza for dinner</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

  </main>

